  "title": "BUSINESS DEVELOPMENT MANAGER",
  "description": "<ul><li>Responsible for seeking new business opportunities through prospecting, qualifying leads, pitching and closing sales.</li><li>Achieve or exceed sales target & meet key performance metrics</li><li>Manage strong client relationship through all phases of sales cycle and securing renewal of existing contracts.</li><li>Prepare sales quotations and tenders.Develop and customise business proposals and conduct presentations to customers.</li><li>Generate new sales and leads to drive revenue growth for the company.</li><li>To ensure delivery of services is in accordance to the contract.</li><li>Supports the development and implementation of annual marketing plan, sales strategies and objectives.</li><li>Monitor and track sales performances, pipeline activities, revenue forecasts.</li></ul><p>For interested applicants, please apply online or send your resume in WORD format to <a href=\"mailto:davidnhbsg@gmail.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>davidnhbsg@gmail.com</strong></a><strong> & ram@deshingroup.com, wayne@deshingroup.com; shawn@deshingroup.com</strong></p><p>Thank you for your application but we regret that only shortlisted candidates will be notified</p>",
